management &amp; control of distributed network systems



this is the home page for the graduate class on management &amp; control of
distributed network systems at columbia university. the class is taught by
dr. joe hellerstein.


teaching assistant: gong su,
623 cepsr, 939-7096. office hour: fri. 2:30-3:30.


